<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Acara Activation User</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap');
    
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f7f9;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05), 0 10px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #2563eb;
      padding: 30px 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .header h1 {
      color: #ffffff;
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    }

    .content {
      padding: 40px;
      color: #374151;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .content p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .content h2 {
      color: #111827;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    ul {
      list-style-type: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 20px 0;
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }

    li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    li:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    li strong {
      color: #111827;
      width: 150px;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .button-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }

    .button {
      background-color: #2563eb;
      color: #ffffff !important;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      display: inline-block;
      transition: background-color 0.2s;
    }

    .button:hover {
      background-color: #1d4ed8;
    }

    .footer {
      background-color: #f9fafb;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }

    .footer p {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6b7280;
      margin: 0;
    }

    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
      .container {
        margin: 20px 10px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }
      li strong {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
      }
    }
  </style>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Selamat Datang</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <p>Halo <strong><%= username %></strong>,</p>
      <p>Terima kasih telah mendaftar di layanan kami. Berikut adalah informasi dari akun Anda:</p>
      
      <h2>Detail Akun</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Nama Lengkap</strong> <%= fullname %></li>
        <li><strong>Email</strong> <%= email %></li>
        <li><strong>Tanggal Daftar</strong> <%= createdAt %></li>
      </ul>
      
      <p>Untuk memulai, silakan klik tombol di bawah ini untuk mengaktifkan akun Anda:</p>
      
      <div class="button-container">
        <a href="<%= activationLink %>" class="button">Aktifkan Akun Sekarang</a>
      </div>
      
      <p>Jika Anda tidak merasa mendaftar di layanan kami, silakan abaikan email ini.</p>
      <p>Hormat kami,<br><strong>Tim Layanan Kami</strong></p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Copyright &copy; 2026 Acara Event Management System. Semua hak cipta dilindungi.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>